1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,115
(Verse 1 – Alarm One)

2
00:00:09,265 --> 00:00:13,381
Alarm goes off, six-thirty-two,

3
00:00:13,531 --> 00:00:17,646
Mom at the door like she always do.

4
00:00:17,796 --> 00:00:21,911
Everything’s fog, ceiling spins,

5
00:00:22,061 --> 00:00:26,177
Then I smile when it sinks in.

6
00:00:26,327 --> 00:00:30,442
It’s just the first one, false alarm,

7
00:00:30,592 --> 00:00:34,707
Still got time, no cause for harm.

8
00:00:34,857 --> 00:00:38,973
World can wait, dreams still hot,

9
00:00:39,123 --> 00:00:43,238
I sink back down into brain rot.

10
00:00:43,388 --> 00:00:47,504
(Verse 2 – Alarm Two)

11
00:00:47,654 --> 00:00:51,769
Alarm again, different tone,

12
00:00:51,919 --> 00:00:56,034
Mom says, “Up,” I half-way groan.

13
00:00:56,184 --> 00:01:00,300
Eyes open now, room comes back,

14
00:01:00,450 --> 00:01:04,565
I scan the floor, my hoodie rack.

15
00:01:04,715 --> 00:01:08,830
Think about school, what day it is,

16
00:01:08,980 --> 00:01:13,096
Sweats or sweats, don’t know which.

17
00:01:13,246 --> 00:01:17,361
Start a plan, then lose the plot,

18
00:01:17,511 --> 00:01:21,626
Slip right back into brain rot.

19
00:01:21,776 --> 00:01:25,892
(Verse 3 – Alarm Three)

20
00:01:26,042 --> 00:01:30,157
Alarm explodes, Mom’s not calm,

21
00:01:30,307 --> 00:01:34,422
Standing there with folded arms.

22
00:01:34,572 --> 00:01:38,688
“This isn’t confusion, it’s a choice”, she
said

23
00:01:38,838 --> 00:01:42,953
Weaponized incompetence ringing in my head

24
00:01:43,103 --> 00:01:47,219
Brain snaps on, stomach drops,

25
00:01:47,369 --> 00:01:51,484
Latin test, declensions, clocks.

26
00:01:51,634 --> 00:01:55,749
I sit straight up, fog gets shot,

27
00:01:55,899 --> 00:02:00,015
No more room for brain rot.

28
00:02:00,165 --> 00:02:04,280
Three alarms to be a person,

29
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:08,545
Mind too soft, attention cursin’.

30
00:02:08,695 --> 00:02:12,811
Morning steals what sleep forgot,

31
00:02:12,961 --> 00:02:17,076
I wake up fighting brain rot.
